<p class="ql-align-center">男子撬锁显得十分娴熟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201208/d98a6bc1bb4c47dc93fca05385d24efe.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不到30秒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">防盗门就被打开了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201208/f431a853e9b14ba291bea54b9968157b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过接下来发生的一幕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让他始料未及</p>
